Titolo: Sometimes Always Monsters

Anno: 2020

Descrizione: Sometimes Always Monsters is a role-playing video game developed and self-published by Vagabond Dog. It is the sequel to the well-received 2014 video game Always Sometimes Monsters.Following events from Always Sometimes Monsters, the player is a recently married author who joins a cross-country bus tour to promote their next novel. Along the way, you there are vicious rumours claiming that the author is a total fraud. Players journey through five unique cities, meet fans and critics alike, and make friends with fellow busmates. Player choices help to unravel the conspiracy laid against the player character.

Genere: Role-playing 

Valutazione: 73
